<p><font size="+2">Q:</font> Having Difficulty Finding your choice ? </p>
<p><font size="+2">A:</font> Its really very easy to locate the jewelry of your 
  choice. We have taken 4 cases and explained each of them here.</p>
<table width="80%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top"><font color="#804040" size="+2">Case 1.</font> If you are 
      looking for a particular stone/metal then go to the home page. On left side 
      of the home page you will see a <em><font color="#004000">vertical menu 
      with a listing of all the stones</font></em> in our collection. Click on 
      the stone of your interest. This will take you to a page that will show 
      you all the jewelry of that stone or metal in our store. See figure and 
      the brown circle.</td>
    <td align="left" valign="top"><img src="images/stonesonlynavigate.gif" width="257" height="256"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p><br>
  <font color="#804040" size="+2">Case 2.</font> If you are looking for a bracelet 
  of a particular stone. Just follow the above steps for case 1 and then on top 
  of the page you will see a <em><font color="#004000">horizontal menu in light 
  green with a list of jewelry types</font></em> available in that stone. Here 
  if you have 'bracelets' written just click on this. See the red circled list 
  in figure below. <img src="images/stoneandtypenavigate.jpg" width="595" height="275"></p>
<table width="80%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top">Alernately, if for examply you are looking for silver bracelets. 
      Just click on the 'bracelets' on the darkgreen horizontal menu on top (You 
      will find this on top of almost every page). On doing this you will see 
      all the bracelets in our store. Now you use the <font color="#004000"><em>vertical 
      menu of stones on left side</em></font> of this page and click on the stone 
      or metal of your choice (in this case silver) tol see only bracelets made 
      of silver.</td>
    <td align="left" valign="top"><img src="images/stonetypenavigate.jpg" width="276" height="297"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br>

<table width="80%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top"><font color="#804040" size="+2">Case 3.</font>If you are 
      looking for say brown pendants. On any page just click on the 'Pendants' 
      written in white on dark green background. Then a page will open up showing 
      you our complete collection of pendants. Now you go to the <font color="#004000"><em>bottom 
      of the page and you will see a drop down to select color and price</em></font><em>.</em> 
      Select the color of your choice. Immediately the page showing only pendants 
      with brown color or whatever you have choosen will show up. </td>
    <td align="center"><img src="images/colornavigate.jpg" width="200" height="260"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p><br>
  <br>
  <font color="#804040" size="+2">Case 4.</font> If you have a budget in mind. 
  Just follow any of the steps explained above and then use the drop down at the 
  bottom that gives you the price ranges. You will be shown jewelry items of that 
  stone/type/color in the desired price range. See figure shown above, you will 
  see the price drop down on right of the color selection dropdown.</p>
<p>Please do write to us to tell us if you faced any difficulty in finding what 
  you wanted. We look forward to improving your shopping experience on our website.<strong>Thankyou 
